        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>Ok, let's see if we can get this script to yell back at us. Run it with:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">php dino_container/roar.php</div></code></pre>
<p>Fantastic! If you don't do anything, Monolog spits your messages out into
stderr.</p>
